Enum PassengerType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<PassengerType>

    public enum PassengerType
extends java.lang.Enum<PassengerType>
    An Enum describing each type of Passenger. Passengers can either be Regular, Rerouted, have Extra Baggage, or be Overbooked.
